Author contributions:
J.B. and M.B.G. designed and coordinated the
study. M.B.G. provided the life-history data. R.O. analyzed the distribution maps and,
together with J.B., developed the network simulations. E.L.R. performed the model selection
and phylogenetic analyses. S.P. ran the species distribution models. All authors contributed
to the discussion of results. J.B. wrote the manuscript with input from all authors.
